Compile under LUNIX
===================

For compilation under LUNIX you need the following software packages:

- Qt 4.3.3 or higher
- SANE 1.0.19 (backends) or higher


Compile DMS - Document Management System
----------------------------------------

- After installing the SANE 1.0.19 backend or higher
	- Get the svn package from http://developer.berlios.de/projects/dms/
		- svn checkout http://svn.berlios.de/svnroot/repos/dms/trunk dmsystem
	- Change after download into this directory and enter the following commands

		qmake
		make
		make install is not needed


Compile under Windows
=====================

Scansupport under Windows is at this time disabled, because i search for better solution as Twain.

For compilation under Windows you need the following software packages:

- Microsoft Visual Studio Express 2005 (optional)
    - Microsoft Platform SDK 2003 R2
	- Qt4 compiled for use with MSVC++
      - Download the latest Qt4 Source Package for Windows (http://www.trolltech.com).
	  - compile it and set the path enviroment QTDIR=/your/qt/direcory without spaces

- MinGW
	- Download the page http://downloads.sourceforge.net/mingw/MinGW-5.1.3.exe?modtime=1168811236&big_mirror=1
	- Qt4 compiled for use with MinGW
      - Download the latest Qt4 Source Package for Windows (http://www.trolltech.com).
	  - compile it and set the path enviroment QTDIR=/your/qt/direcory without spaces


Compile DMS - Document Management System
----------------------------------------

You need the svn binary for Windows.

- MSVC++ 2005
	- Get the svn package from http://developer.berlios.de/projects/dms/
		- svn checkout http://svn.berlios.de/svnroot/repos/dms/trunk dmsystem
	- Change after download into this directory
	- Open the solution file (dms.sln) in the dmsystem directory and compile it

- MinGW
	- Change after download into this directory
	- Open the commandline from Windows (Start->Run->cmd / Start->AusfÃ¼hren->cmd)
		- The MinGW path enviroment must set.

	qmake
	mingw32-make


Have you trouble with installation or you found problems of DMS please send to dms-bugreport@lists.berlios.de and not directly to me.
Have you trouble with installation and/or configuration of SANE please send to http://alioth.debian.org/mail/?group_id=30186 and not to me.


